[SN]TITLE[SN]
Snow windscreen driver: Man charged with motoring offence

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been charged after a driver was filmed with a windscreen almost completely obscured by snow in Aberdeenshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident was captured on a dash cam on the B9119 near Garlogie.
It showed the vehicle with only a small circle of snow cleared.
Police Scotland said a 36-year-old man had now been charged with a driving offence in relation to the incident which happened at about 07:45 on Monday 15 February.
